Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Garm Phoenix, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can be revived so many times!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, how to defeat you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Garm Phoenix suit actor is Fighter Tanaka who had retracted his retirement statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly decided to take the leading role. \NThat's the story behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(630.857,482.429)}March 6{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're so well-informed.\N- What was that again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- The protagonist's signature phrase...?\N- It's time to go back to your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will start my class today.\NBow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs37}[We've been deceived by Sensei. Lol]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who posted this on SNS this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to post anything on SNS until further instruction is issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, I got so many followers...\N- That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's make it more exciting, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Hiiragi Ibuki's post?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also flustered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't believe he treats us like criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have any clue?\N- Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just his trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei is calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Camera! Get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Hiiragi-sen...sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'll pick it up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please let the other teachers hear my voice too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been surprised at my sudden announcement the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Spreading that kind of rumor!\N- It's not a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you is the culprit who asked Bermuzu to make Kageyama Reina's fake video.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have seen the attached customers list's image too, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! None of us is the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also wanted to think like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, today, I would like to give you a task!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A task?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want the "hunter", who had asked Berumuzu{\i0} to make Kageyama Reina's fake video, to confess at 8 pm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that person doesn't confess, I will blow up the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you saying?!\N-  {\i1}Our students' lives...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...depend on you, guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for the good news!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I said. \NI'll blow up the class if the "hunter" doesn't confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will evacuate us first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're on the same team, aren't we?\N- Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of becoming your alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to cooperate with me by offering you lives, so that I could find the truth. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stop using your phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's risky to let you keep your phones after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna collect your bags and phones now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel somewhat nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is the last!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't kill us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,, I'm afraid I have to do that if they can't fulfill my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If none of the teachers confesses as the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will die?\N- Binggo! As an ex insider, you're truly understand this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I feel sorry for you because all you can do is wait without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do you guys want to try persuading your teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can touch the culprit's heart by begging desperately for your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not see things only from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not ignore the essence..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Berumuzu was asked to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard about it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...from that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI'm sorry to bother you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- I need to talk to Fumika-san about something.\N- I won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please go.\N- Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Fumika-san think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was probably her fault that this barricade incident happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Even if you ask me that...\N- Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why can't you tell him?\N- Just get back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibuki is doing that for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then, isn't it better to tell the detective...\N- Can you just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't bother us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting from now, I'm going to look for the culprit who requested Reina's fake video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you the moderator, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back to being a slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She volunteered herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to find out the truth about Reina,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should move first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to your opinions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we end up with these 5 candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't think the principal is one of them.\N- Well, he could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the principal was complaining about Kageyama before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was annoyed by the press that kept coming in and out to visit a star athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's call him "Jay White".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jay?\N- Jay white?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The next suspect is Morisaki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Morisaki-sensei was interested in Bookie, so, there's a possibility.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand women~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's cute about you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she thought of Kageyama as her rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,she could be the one who ordered the fake video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she is "Juice Robinson".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been labeling them as "Jay White", "Juice Robinson"..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're the wrestlers of NJPW*.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(621.714,87)}* New Japan Pro Wrestling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be easier to compare them with the New Japan Cup's candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't understand! Just do it normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about the 3rd candidate : Sakuma-sensei...?\N- To put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Ah~ That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to smirk at Reina a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to make Kageyama mine and mine only."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to possess her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a 'circle'*!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(633.143,87)}* A 'Yes' symbol{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The next candidate is Takechi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any relation between Takechi and Reina, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He was hitting on her quite passionately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the recommendation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was asked if she wanted to get recommended to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in the end, she chose a different desired college,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so that story started to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seo was also getting a recommended by Takechi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Takechi is the type who's just "all talk, no result".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural for him to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an 'X' mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one : Tsuboi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's the most suspicious one, right?\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one behind our powerful swimming club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't it better to ask the swimming club members?\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a harsh personality indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There were quite a lot of students who were afraid of Tsuboi-sensei and decided to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Btw, Suzune, you were in swimming club too before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the summer of 2nd grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to throw up just by thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That far?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the reason?\N- I was caught dating with Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was spreading out our pictures in front everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, " I don't need you."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He changed his attitude towards his favorite student because she had a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was interested in Reina too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Reina didn't like him, he made that fake video...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's no proof.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina was able to meet Sensei's expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I wasn't able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- I didn't mean...\N- If you're an underachiever, you have no right to talk big like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know how I felt when I had to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait a minute!\N- Wait! Karen! Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm from class 1C, my name is Minakoshi Suzune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Not only she's cute, but also the top prize winner in the city center district.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm from class 1B, my name is Kageyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's Kageyama Reina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard she's at the national level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't lose focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move your whole body more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Improve your next move!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Do one more lap!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsuboi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so enthusiastic about Minakoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard she's also getting closer to Reina's record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- You've been waiting?\N- I'm already used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Going home late again after practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I don't want to lose to Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My chest has been hurting lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyakoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting tomorrow, you don't have to come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last monday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you ditch practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I didn't ditch it...\N- You were with Nakao, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A flirting girl like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if you come to practice, you will only annoy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...coach you again for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yosh! Let's start the practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get caught, you'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you obey my words?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The culprit is you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I the culprit??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said you did it, Morisaki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But your eyes say otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the students hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, after all, the culprit is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}..probably you..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuboi-sensei gets more hate from the students than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the rumor! There are a lot of sexual and power harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- You're the culprit.{\i0}\N- Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained them like that to make them stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say that you did it purely for the students??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:19:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you saying that you are somehow the culprit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who benefits from this drama??!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to take our dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ladies' room!\NIsn't that voyeurism?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the washroom.\NBe quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakoshi-san and Yuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a Class-3A student at Kaio High School, a former swimming club member, Minakoshi Suzune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The swimming club's adviser, Tsuboi-sensei, had been sexually harassing and abusing his power over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As soon as he knew that I was dating this one guy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he didn't let me practice anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was forced to quit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think he must have done the same thing to Reina, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person behind the fake video,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,must be Tsuboi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That video,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,please upload it on Mind Voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really true, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Tsuboi will never turn himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using the internet to corner him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't admit that he's the culprit, we will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you post that video, you'll get a lot of followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get a lot of attention too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Tsuboi-sensei really the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, how much do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the person who drove Reina into suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many questions! \NCan you just narrow it down to 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...to catch the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about dinner? Your friends are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...believe in you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi Ibuki's origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He worked at the movie studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his part time job while still an art school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(633.143,64.143)}*Special effects{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628.572,690.429)}He seemed to be in charge of doing the modeling for Tokusatsu* heroes and monsters' designs, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he also started acting as a suit actor that relied so much on physical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,, Suit actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a "suit actor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a "suit actor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those words are only used in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we hide our faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we're still actors after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,... a fighter, Tanaka-san, he's a legend of Tokusatsu* world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(633.143,64.143)}*Special effects{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokusatsu movie that Fighter Tanaka and Hiiragi Ibuki co-starred in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...is this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"IVKI" is written here. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he also a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. \NHe was a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That yellow one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was Hiiragi Ibuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a serious guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Both acting and action, he did it very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked like a person who would never commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the world turned into his enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he would still fight for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like a Hero of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after this thing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you still can believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He has strong muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought about retiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hand over the leading role to him in the next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Garm Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the main actor is certainly you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He has stopped acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he gave up being an action actor. \NAnd with Fumika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taking the same path as his teacher girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By "Fumika-chan", do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sagara Fumika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.76,0:24:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I know her or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,she's our President's daughter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.24,0:24:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the company president of this movie studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagara Takahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.64,0:25:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.74,0:25:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These things...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.. Do you know whether these were made here or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.64,0:25:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your number one suspect is Tsuboi-sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Minakoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your video.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.08,0:25:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It caused amazing reactions on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.96,0:25:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What video?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.64,0:25:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a Class-3A student at Kaio High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a former swimming club member, Minakoshi Suzune.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.92,0:25:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The swimming club's adviser, Tsuboi-sensei, had been sexually harassing and abusing his power over me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.96,0:25:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person behind the fake video,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.10,0:25:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}must be Tsuboi-sensei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.16,0:25:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once people see this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.44,0:25:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they must think of Tsuboi-sensei as the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.54,0:26:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.50,0:26:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell any lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.32,0:26:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only stating my opinions!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.82,0:26:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.54,0:26:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...  People are bashing Tsuboi-sensei all over the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.12,0:26:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves him right...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.68,0:26:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you connected to the internet?\N- Yeah. Somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.20,0:26:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei also wanted to make a video call so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.30,0:26:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has been on edge since a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.14,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They even fought with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.82,0:26:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be calm now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.38,0:26:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give out my photo album that will be released tomorrow, finally it....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.94,0:26:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.88,0:26:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doodling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.62,0:26:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of drawing skill is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.68,0:26:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing with these pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.26,0:27:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It will pierce through the next pages too...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.04,0:27:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You look very calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.40,0:27:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.84,0:27:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of customers list can't be used as an evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.92,0:27:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-Sensei is calling!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.28,0:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guys~!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Long time no see~!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.10,0:27:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost 8 pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.90,0:27:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who asked Berumuzu to make Kageyama Reina's fake video, a.k.a "hunter"-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.00,0:27:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please come forward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.82,0:27:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei, I don't know what kind of joke you're pulling now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no such a person here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.48,0:27:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that so? What a pity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.94,0:27:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.40,0:27:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will blow up the class now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.02,0:27:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.18,0:27:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's talk about it properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.00,0:27:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiiragi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.98,0:28:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop doing stupid things! Do you think you can get away after doing something like this??!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.46,0:28:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuboi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.26,0:28:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.82,0:28:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...who can't get away so easily~!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.18,0:28:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.18,0:28:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the students' predictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tusboi-sensei seems to be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.62,0:28:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Minakoshi! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.26,0:28:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Tsuboi-sensei is the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to persuade him yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.06,0:28:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.42,0:28:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who asked Berumuzu to make Reina's fake video, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.28,0:28:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I could never do that...!{\i0}\N- Tell me honestly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.54,0:29:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwhise, we will die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.54,0:29:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I told you it's not me!{\i0}\N- You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.52,0:29:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you pushed me into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.42,0:29:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you must have done it to Reina too!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was only that one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.84,0:29:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was absent from practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I only went to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you snatch away swimming from me??
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.36,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.34,0:29:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked harder than everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.78,0:29:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.16,0:29:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minakoshi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.56,0:29:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt annoyed by my relationship with Ren, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You kicked me out because you couldn't have me, right??
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.68,0:30:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Reina, because you knew she wasn't interested in you, you decided to corner her just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.48,0:30:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.22,0:30:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.34,0:30:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.84,0:30:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsuboi-sensei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.44,0:30:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.24,0:30:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should tell her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.98,0:30:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.28,0:30:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...by "The truth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.36,0:30:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the truth? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.14,0:31:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you worked harder than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.22,0:31:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every single day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You practiced till late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.54,0:31:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In muscle training too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.26,0:31:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}among the students I trained,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.44,0:31:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you were the most hard-working one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.86,0:31:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.14,0:31:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wouldn't do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.44,0:31:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.58,0:31:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.80,0:31:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were absent from practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.80,0:31:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your mom contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.96,0:31:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were both...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.36,0:31:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...listening to your doctor's explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.98,0:31:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suzune-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.46,0:31:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...suffers from exercise-induced lethal arrhythmia*.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.46,0:31:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(628.572,68.715)}*Life-threatening abnormal heartbeats that are triggered by exercise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lethal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.48,0:32:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The arrhythmia was caused by excessive practice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.24,0:32:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she keeps practicing like that, I'm afraid it may cause her to faint and go into cardiac arrest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.34,0:32:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, please prevent her from doing heavy exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.92,0:32:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.98,0:32:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.44,0:32:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is going to take part in the next tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.82,0:32:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow I want her to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.82,0:32:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.50,0:32:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she keeps being an athlete, she may lose her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.06,0:32:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was asked by your mother to persuade you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She said even if she told you to stop,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.78,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you would still take part in the tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.10,0:32:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought you would do the same even if I was the one who told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.98,0:33:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...any other way than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.76,0:33:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.86,0:33:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you did it all for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.66,0:33:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.02,0:33:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.28,0:33:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you were hurt because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.62,0:33:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.68,0:33:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel cheated...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you only telling me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.08,0:34:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to his explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.38,0:34:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,do you still suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.30,0:34:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.92,0:34:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about my own health and what Sensei was suffering from!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.26,0:34:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.26,0:34:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...mistakenly resented Tsuboi-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.14,0:34:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and took that video.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.84,0:34:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.20,0:34:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With that video...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.46,0:34:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.68,0:34:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This video wasn't posted on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.26,0:34:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped Yuki just before she posted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\frz344.1\pos(820.572,539.572)}[The truth about a Kaio High School's teacher.]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.34,0:34:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a pity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.46,0:35:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuki, bring your phone here right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.24,0:35:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.68,0:35:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me not to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.54,0:35:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.60,0:35:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it a relief??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.16,0:35:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it a relief ?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.44,0:35:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.00,0:35:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...you tried to spread that video all over the internet doesn't change, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.50,0:35:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- Don't say "but"!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.92,0:36:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If that video spread all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.48,0:36:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen to Tsuboi-sensei??
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.48,0:36:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you carefully thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.18,0:36:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.88,0:36:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.84,0:36:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your careless statements,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.58,0:36:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You could turn innocent people into someone they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.26,0:36:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stigmatize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.70,0:36:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His family!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.04,0:36:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They could have been hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.20,0:36:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.30,0:36:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...tried to do something that can never be recovered, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand??
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.92,0:36:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.48,0:36:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't happen in the end, please forgive her already!\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.22,0:36:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Suzune has showed her regret...\N- Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.16,0:36:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "it couldn't be helped"? Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.44,0:37:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "regret"???
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see things halfheartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE CHANGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.22,0:37:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.34,0:37:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't only see things from the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.00,0:37:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully!!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.78,0:37:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.28,0:37:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See it properly with your eyes!\NPut it in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.90,0:37:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Carve it in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.52,0:37:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do that, you will keep repeating the same mistake over and over again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.14,0:37:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn away from the essence, it won't work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.54,0:37:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Minakoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.40,0:37:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening? I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.80,0:37:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakoshi, Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.68,0:37:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you put it properly in your head? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.66,0:37:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you properly carved it in your heart? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.78,0:38:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.70,0:38:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...are not at the age where...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.34,0:38:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can make mistakes based on your emotions anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.84,0:38:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not at the age to be allowed to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.98,0:38:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.14,0:38:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Think! Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.14,0:38:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.82,0:38:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.90,0:38:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own words!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.54,0:38:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more responsible for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.88,0:38:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.70,0:38:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your single foolish word...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.66,0:38:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...might be able to save someone.\N But, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.88,0:38:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget that someone might get hurt too because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A single word from you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.88,0:38:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...could easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.76,0:39:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...take someone else's life!\NDon't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.18,0:39:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.00,0:39:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys too, don't ever forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.54,0:39:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry to keep you waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.22,0:39:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just gave them a good lesson thanks to all of you~!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.06,0:39:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.78,0:39:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A promise is a promise..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As a punishment for not confessing to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.62,0:39:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will blow up the class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.44,0:40:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't I tell you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.12,0:40:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for not fulfilling my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.36,0:40:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.64,0:40:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.06,0:40:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Until 8 pm, it's... {\i1}5!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.62,0:40:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hiiragi! Stop it!\N{\i1}- 4!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.62,0:40:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}3!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.94,0:40:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hiiragi-sensei!\N{\i1}- 2!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.94,0:40:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.46,0:40:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}1!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.78,0:40:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.88,0:40:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.62,0:40:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.34,0:40:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your feelings towards your murdered students?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.04,0:40:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,HIIIIRRAGIIIII!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.32,0:41:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding~!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take a closer look at the blasted classroom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.76,0:41:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's class 3B!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.14,0:41:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The students are safe. Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.02,0:41:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.96,0:41:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do people all over the world think about you, who had been running away to protect yourself until the students were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.66,0:41:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\frz3.979\pos(649.142,418.429)}[Self-protection is more important than their students' lives.]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.14,0:41:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\frz358.2\pos(610.286,379.572)}Such shitty teachers. LOL{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.34,0:41:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\frz4.145\pos(598.857,411.571)}[I think I understood what Hiiragi Ibuki is fighting for.]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.68,0:41:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.92,0:41:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprising us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.10,0:41:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.84,0:41:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.10,0:41:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei has...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.86,0:41:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...given us the hint perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.10,0:41:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.22,0:41:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we will start the game 'Believe it or Not'~!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.40,0:42:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.22,0:42:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Believe me when I'm wearing my glasses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.10,0:42:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't believe me when I take them off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.44,0:42:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Understood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.50,0:42:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.24,0:42:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...was telling lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.54,0:42:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he wasn't wearing his glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.10,0:42:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been noticing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.70,0:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, did you notice from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.14,0:42:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You should have told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.36,0:42:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have told us sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.04,0:42:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.94,0:42:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.22,0:42:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sensei wanted you to notice it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When he said "think carefully",
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.60,0:42:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't only see things from the surface",
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.24,0:42:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do not ignore the essence."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.84,0:42:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.64,0:43:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Garm Phoenix's signature phrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.40,0:43:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.08,0:43:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.54,0:43:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,During the past month, Sagara Takahiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.18,0:43:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...seems to have ordered some sculpted objects, and bought a large amount of explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.54,0:43:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.90,0:43:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi Ibuki and Sagara Takahiko are...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.12,0:43:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...related.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.10,0:43:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.46,0:43:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(635.429,704.143)}Today is Tuesday, September 25.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.08,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\pos(173.714,523.571)}What video is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs37\pos(674.286,647)}[Is this the moment where Kageyama Reina committed suicide?]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.54,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\pos(340.571,180.715)}[The man wearing a hat is the culprit?]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\pos(322.286,311)}[Did he possibly kill Kageyama Reina???]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.62,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs40\pos(635.429,441.286)}[Is that the "hunter"!?]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.32,0:43:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally tracked you down, "hunter"-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.00,0:44:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.64,0:44:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Takechi Yamato-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.76,0:44:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.32,0:44:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's think!{\i0}
